{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1975730/extras/LogoSized.png?t=1675443266\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Paranormal investigation game.</h2>The Grimoire hides many secrets and information precious to arcane investigators.<br>Search for magical creatures, rare animals and the hidden world in this simulation game.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1975730/extras/Creatures.png?t=1675443266\" /><br><br>Have you ever wondered what lurks in the forest? In addition to birds and rabbits, what really hides.<br>What if I told you the legends are true. All that told through generations really exists and today with this Grimoire you will be able to find them.<br>Join the Guild of Arcane Investigators, experts in mystical creatures and the occult, delve into the forest for clues and information and find out what we're up to.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1975730/extras/HolderBeast.png?t=1675443266\" /><br><br>Dragons, fairies and werewolves, any of them could be behind the bush, choose the right equipment and find out fast what you are hunting or the prey could be you.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1975730/extras/Equip.png?t=1675443266\" /><br><br>Magic Crystals, Lanterns and Compasses, the guild will provide everything you need, but of course it comes at a price, bring scales, fur and other evidence they cost a lot in the arcane market.<br>The equipment is extremely useful in your hunts.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1975730/extras/HolderItem.png?t=1675443266\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1975730/extras/Evidence.png?t=1675443266\" /><br><br>To find out which creature is in the region you must be very attentive to the clues left by it, a tuft of fur, claw marks, footprints and several other clues will guide you to success.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1975730/extras/HolderClue.png?t=1675443266\" /><br><br>Observing the clues left by the creature it is possible to discover its species.<br>A noise, a claw mark, a footprint, all of these are crucial when it comes to investigating, stick to the details, observe with extreme care, note the evidence, and rush to take action.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1975730/extras/EarlyAccess.png?t=1675443266\" /><br><br>Why Early Access?<br><br>The game is already at an advanced stage of development but there are still important choices to be made, we hope to build an active community that helps make these decisions, suggestions and ideas are very welcome and will be taken seriously.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":" Introduction to Arcanism","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1975730/82aab238cb1a4ee415edad91a0053950e354a7a3.jpg"},{"name":"Supernatural","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1975730/82aab238cb1a4ee415edad91a0053950e354a7a3.jpg"},{"name":"Gotta catch them all","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1975730/82aab238cb1a4ee415edad91a0053950e354a7a3.jpg"},{"name":"Arcanophobia.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1975730/82aab238cb1a4ee415edad91a0053950e354a7a3.jpg"},{"name":"Right on target.","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1975730/82aab238cb1a4ee415edad91a0053950e354a7a3.jpg"},{"name":"It's a trap","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1975730/82aab238cb1a4ee415edad91a0